[0m[49m[39m  250, 252[0m:[39m[49m             FOR each concept in entity.RxNormConcepts:
[0m[49m[39m  251, 253[0m:[39m[49m                 IF concept.Score >= RXNORM_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD:
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 252     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m                     // Record the mapping: text as detected, RxNorm ID, human-readable description
