[0m[49m[39m  441, 441[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  442, 442[0m:[39m[49m     DetectEntitiesV2 is trained on clinical and pharmaceutical text. When you
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 443     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m     pass it "Lisinopril 10mg", it identifies the MEDICATION entity, pulls out
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 444     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m     dosage as an attribute, and returns RxNorm concept IDs for the detected
